@startuml
!include ../../style.puml

title Chaos Engineering Tests Resilience Under Fault

actor Alice
participant athens
participant byzantium
participant cyrene
participant Nemesis

Alice -> athens : set("title", "Microservices")
activate athens
Nemesis ->x cyrene : kill node / cut network
athens -> byzantium : replicate write
activate byzantium
byzantium --> athens : ack
deactivate byzantium
athens ->x cyrene : replicate write
athens --> Alice : success
deactivate athens

note bottom #E6F3FF
Focus:
does the system stay available
and recover under fault?
end note

@enduml
